  "detailed_description": "Caliper 2 is an absolute, turn-based puzzle. By manipulating objects with different properties, you need to put some object on the button and enter the portal. Objects have both common and unique properties. Every 5 levels an object is added with unique properties, the combination of which gives a variety of solutions to riddles.<br />\r\nStone as the simplest object.<br />\r\nBlocks glide over the snow.<br />\r\nIce is like snow, but you can kick it.<br />\r\nCart carries blocks. Rubble will not allow ice to slide.<br />\r\nCoal will melt the snow and ice.<br />\r\nThe freezer will turn everything into ice.<br />\r\nFlamethrower will melt the ice.<br />\r\nThe twins copy each other's movements.",
